《'''錦繡豪門'''》（{{lang-en|''Dynasty''}}）是一部美国[[黃金時段|黃金時段]]电视[[肥皂剧|肥皂剧]]。从1981年1月12日至1989年5月11日在[[美国广播公司|ABC频道]]播出。由理查德和埃丝特·夏皮罗原创，[[艾倫·斯班林|艾倫·斯班林]]制作。该剧围绕着居住在[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[丹佛|丹佛]]的一个[[虚构作品|虚构]]的富裕家族卡林顿展开。<ref name="SOE">{{Cite book |last=Schemering |first=Christopher |authorlink=Christopher Schemering |title=The Soap Opera Encyclopedia |url=https://archive.org/details/soapoperaencyclo0000sche_z6n5 |date=September 1985 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/soapoperaencyclo0000sche_z6n5/page/80 80]–81 |isbn=0-345-32459-5}}</ref>由{{link-en|约翰·福赛斯|John Forsythe}}饰演石油大亨布莱克·卡林顿，[[琳达·埃文斯|琳达·埃文斯]]饰演他的新任妻子。<ref name="SOE"/><ref name="Forsythe Time">{{Cite news |title=Charlie's an Angel Now: John Forsythe Dies at 92 |publisher=Time.com |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]'' magazine |date=2010-04-03 |url=http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1977623,00.html#ixzz0yITk3bNe |accessdate=2010-09-25 |first=Richard |last=Corliss |archive-date=2010-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101119180318/http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1977623,00.html#ixzz0yITk3bNe |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

该剧第一季收视一般，但到了第二季[[瓊·考琳絲|瓊·考琳絲]]加入饰演布莱克诡计多端的前妻后收视率进入前20<ref name="SOE"/><ref name="Slate">{{Cite news |title=The ''Dynasty'' That Could Have Been |publisher=State.com |work=Slate |date=2011-05-25 |url=http://www.slate.com/id/2293600/ |accessdate=2011-05-27 |first=Alex |last=Mar |archive-date=2011-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906021429/http://www.slate.com/id/2293600 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Directory Ratings">{{cite book|last=Brooks|first=Tim|author2=Earle Marsh|title=The Complete Directory to Prime Time Network and Cable TV Shows|url=https://archive.org/details/completedirector0000broo_y4r5|date=October 2007|edition=9th|pages=[https://archive.org/details/completedirector0000broo_y4r5/page/1689 1689]–1692|chapter=Top-Rated Programs by Season|isbn=978-0-345-49773-4}}</ref><ref name="Ratings 1982">{{cite web|url=http://www.classictvhits.com/tvratings/1981.htm|title=ClassicTVHits.com: TV Ratings > 1980's|work=classictvhits.com|accessdate=2015-02-27|archive-date=2013-01-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DXB1ZiPv?url=http://www.classictvhits.com/tvratings/1981.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1982年秋季排名前10，1985年春季收视获得全美国第一。<ref name="Directory Ratings"/><ref name="Ratings 1985">{{cite web|url=http://www.classictvhits.com/tvratings/1984.htm|title=ClassicTVHits.com: TV Ratings > 1980's|publisher=|accessdate=2015-04-20|archive-date=2015-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151217053950/http://www.classictvhits.com/tvratings/1984.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他著名的剧组成员包括苏帕梅拉·马丁，劳埃德·波切内尔，希瑟·洛克利尔，迈克尔·纳德，艾玛·萨姆斯，泰德·麦克金尼，洛克·哈德森，凯特·奥马拉和斯蒂芬妮·比彻姆。

1981年到1986年《錦繡豪門》每年都获得[[金球奖|金球奖]]最佳电视剧的提名，并于1984年获奖。<ref name="1984 Globe Winners">{{cite web|url=http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/award_show/golden_globe_awards/1984|title=The 1984 Golden Globe Award Winners|publisher=RopeofSilicon.com|accessdate=2010-01-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/664ymQnEE?url=http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/award_show/golden_globe_awards/1984/|archivedate=2012-03-11}}</ref>该系列最后两季收视大幅下降<ref name="Directory Ratings"/>，它最终在1989年春天播出了九季共220集后被取消。<ref name="People 1991-08-05">{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20115641,00.html|title=Alexis Strikes Again!|last=Gliatto|first=Tom|author2=Vicki Sheff|date=1991-08-05|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|publisher=Vol. 36, No. 4|pages=66–68|accessdate=2009-02-21|archive-date=2009-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318195308/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20115641,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1991年10月播出了该剧的两个衍生迷你剧。<ref name="People 1991-08-05"/>

